er, recipe developer, and photographer at Dora's Table and Mi Mero Mole. Born and raised in Mexico and a graduate of the Culinary Institute of America in New York, she adopted a vegan (plant-based) diet to take control of her health.","sameAs":["https://dorastable.com/about/about-me/"],"url":"https://dorastable.com/author/dora-l-stonegmail-com/"},{"@context":"http://schema.org/","@type":"Recipe","name":"Vegan Fresas con Crema","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dora S."},"description":"These Fresas con Crema are sweet, tangy, delicious, and completely vegan!","datePublished":"2020-08-22T07:12:53+00:00","image":["https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fresas-con-crema-5.jpg","https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fresas-con-crema-5-500x500.jpg","https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fresas-con-crema-5-500x375.jpg","https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fresas-con-crema-5-480x270.jpg"],"recipeYield":["4","4 servings"],"prepTime":"PT30M","totalTime":"PT1470M","recipeIngredient":["1 cup Almonds (soaked overnight, peeled)","½ cup Almond milk (unsweetened)","1 tsp. Vanilla extract","1 tsp. Lemon juice, fresh","¼ cup Agave syrup","1/3-1/2 cup Water","1 lb. Strawberries (hulled and cut into quarters)"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"To make the almond crema pour boiling water over almonds and let them soak overnight. The next day peel the almonds. Place an almond between your thumb and your forefinger and press slightly. The skin should slip right off.","name":"To make the almond crema pour boiling water over almonds and let them soak overnight. The next day peel the almonds. Place an almond between your thumb and your forefinger and press slightly. The skin should slip right off.","url":"https://dorastable.com/vegan-fresas-con-crema/#wprm-recipe-8207-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Place almond in a blender with almond milk, vanilla, lemon juice, agave, and 1/3 cup of water.","name":"Place almond in